privateJob.title: Ford India Notification 2021 – Opening for Various Software Engineer Posts
privateJob.body:
Name of the post:

  • Software Engineer

Description:

Ford India has issued a notification to fill the vacancies of various posts of Software Engineer. If you are finding jobs in Chennai then feel free to apply online from The ProGrad .The candidates who are interested in the vacancies issued by Ford India can see the detailed information about key skills required, educational qualification, total vacancies, how to apply, roles, and responsibilities are given below. Ford India is dealing with Automobile products. If you are interested then read the details that are given below.

Total vacancies:

  • Various vacancies have released.

Selection Process:

  • Written test
  • Group Discussion
  • Personal Interview

Role and responsibility:

  • Translate product strategy into detailed requirements 
  • Can clearly communicate product vision/strategy to team members and stakeholders.
  • Attend the required workshops to understand the product roadmap
  • Responsible for developing product features, prioritizing the backlog, and managing risks while ensuring the iterations and releases are meeting the business objectives
  • These are some of the roles and responsibilities for one post. You should check for each post shown in apply now link

Application fee:

  • No information is given about the application required.

Educational qualification:

The candidates who are interested to apply for the Ford India job must have the following qualification:

  • The candidates must have completed the B.E., B.Tech, MCA  from a recognized university to apply for the application Ford India Notification 2021

Key skills required :

The candidates who are interested to apply in these job openings must have the following key skills that are required to do this:

  • Experience in Agile principles & practices 
  • Proficient in using Rally/JIRA
  • Willing to work in NA Time zone
  • Excellent customer interaction & communication skills
  • Prior experience handling major programs/products involving multiple stakeholders
  • Check it out on apply now link shown above for more.

Payscale info. :

  • The Payscale information will be decided at the time of the interview.

The document needs to be carried:

The candidates who will be selected for the interview must carry the below-mentioned documents:

  • The first and foremost thing is your resume/CV which has your educational background and other related information.
  • You must have your Adhaar card for identity purposes.
  • You must have other identity proofs like a PAN card, voter id, or Passport to prove your citizenship.
  • At last, you should have photocopies of important educational certificates.

How to apply for Ford India Notification 2021?

Candidates who are eligible and interested to apply for Ford India  Job then you should follow the below steps to apply:

  • Note: You can also apply by clicking the apply now button shown above to apply directly from here
  • First of all, read the Ford India Notification 2021 notification thoroughly at the official website india.ford.com.
  • You should have an email id and a phone number for communication purposes.
  • Click on the apply now link for the post you want to apply for.
  • Fill in the required details and submit.
  • Pay the application fee asked for.
  • Finally submit and download the application form for future purposes.
